latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have been using this since my childhood! It’s super easy, you need not spend anything for this! You’ll simply get all stuff at your home in your kitchen! And yes anyone can use this you, your mom, your dad, your bro anyone👻👻 Most importantly all credits to my sisters for helping me and doing my braids☺️ also my baby sis - Baabu for holding my camera through out the video and filming shots again and again so that I could do the best🙏🏻🙏🏻 Do try this and let me know how was the result 🥰 Also you can use this on alternate days for that regular glow🤩
